Description: The lead singer and main creative force behind Huntr/x, Rumi fights with a sword that she can make magically appear. She also is half demon and is embarrassed about that
The creative director for the visual effects behind Huntr/x, Mira was always a bad girl growing up but now has friends and fights demons with a sharp thing on the end of a stick!
Zoey is Huntr/x' main lyricist and she fights demons with some knife things she throws. She is from Berkeley California and is very much a people pleaser.
Jinu is the lead singer of Saja Boys and also a demon. Long ago he betrayed his family due to Gwi-ma's evil influence, but he is good now.
Bobby is Huntr/X's manager. He is good at booming venues but not good at realizing that the band he manages is also a demon fighting team.
